(24, 21, 'FRAUD CHECK RECIEVED.. NEED HELP...', ',5,', '', '', 0, 'I recieved a check in the mail, though it was legit, cashed it. A few days later we recieve a call from bank saying it was no good. Said to come in make arrangments, well a few days later after arrangments made, they told us the saginaw township detectives wanted to handle situation. The check was for $4,950 Honestly I THOUGH IT WAS LEGIT or I never would have cashed it and spent the money. My wife works part time, and I am a college student at the Univeristy of Phoenix and need help. They contacted us yesterday to come in for a interview today, we called to make sure detective was their he was not, left message for him to call us and come in, I am not quite sure what to do, go in and plead my case? or not and face the charges? I feel as if I am the victom in this situation. PLEASE HELP! WE CANNOT afford to GO TO JAIL or get FELONIES, I am going for CRIMINAL JUSTICE and my wife is going for NURSING. We also have 2 small childern we need to be around for...', '', '', 0, NULL, 0, 2, 567, 4, '2009-11-18 17:44:47', '2009-11-22 17:44:47', 0, 0, 1, '', 3, '2009-11-19 05:14:47', 0, '0.00', ''),
(25, 22, 'i want to get custody of my child', ',2,', '', '', 0, 'In aug of 06 my ex & I separated when he left the house he took our daughter & has had physical custody of her ever since. At first custody wasnt an issue she lived with him but I could see her when ever & as long as I wanted. In sept of 07 I had to move from NC to WA because I had no where to stay anymore. Since I moved custody has been a major issue & hes only allowed me to see her once since then which was in April of 08. Everytime im suppose to be able to have her at the last minute he backs out & says I cant have her & his fiance is now the primary caretaker of him because hes gone out of the house for up to 3 days at a time & is now trying to do contracting overseas which will have him out of the house for a yr & hes leaving our daughter with his fiance. I just want to establish some kind of custody of my daughter. Id like to be the primary but since shes been with him for so long I know thats a long shot. Ill be happy with anything I just want to be able to see her. I feel like hes trying to keep me out of our daughters life he already has her calling his fiance mom & last time I saw her she wouldnt even call me mom.', '', '819file_download_script.zip', 0, NULL, 345, 56, 3456, 3, '2009-11-19 15:54:26', '2009-11-22 15:54:26', 0, 1, 0, '', 1, '2009-11-20 03:24:26', 0, '0.00', ''),
(26, 22, 'Custody,Divorce Case', ',2,9,', '', '', 0, 'My wife and I have been seperated for 2yrs.  We have a 4yr old daughter.  My daughter had been residing her mother and my sister in an apartment that i was paying for in Gilbert.  I have been residing in my townhome.tOn Aug 28th there was an issue at my wifes apartment.  My sister witnessed my daughter run out of her moms bedroom into her arms.  She claimed that her mom was trying to hurt her.  I was called over to the apartment.  I had words with my wife, informing her that i would have to get cps involved to investigate matters of abuse that have been being alleged for quite some time. ', '', '', 0, NULL, 6789, 0, 234, 5, '2009-11-19 16:30:34', '2009-12-24 16:30:34', 1, 0, 1, '', 3, '2009-11-20 04:00:34', 0, '0.00', ''),
(27, 22, 'Terms of Service', ',15,', '', '', 0, 'My wife and I have been seperated for 2yrs.  We have a 4yr old daughter.  My daughter had been residing her mother and my sister in an apartment that i was paying for in Gilbert.  I have been residing in my townhome. <p>On Aug 28th there was an issue at my wifes apartment.  My sister witnessed my daughter run out of her moms bedroom into her arms.  She claimed that her mom was trying to hurt her.  I was called over to the apartment.  I had words with my wife, informing her that i would have to get cps involved to investigate matters of abuse that have been being alleged for quite some time. <p>I took my daughter for the weekend, to the disapproval of her mom.  My daughter had expressed that she did not want to go home and that she was afraid of her mom.  On the 31st of August, my wife was not home and so I dropped my daughter off with my sister who resided with my wife in the apartment.  That was the last time I saw my daughter.<p>I later learned that she was in domestic violence shelters claiming emotional abuse. <p>On 9/16/09 i filed for divorce, Temporary order papers, as well as an Emergency Petition.  I was given a hearing scheduled for 9/23/09 and was advised to try to find my wife to get her served for that date.  My wife was hiding in D.V shelters and her where abouts were unknown so when i went to court 9/23/09  she was not there.<p>', '', '', 0, NULL, 0, 0, 1456, 7, '2009-11-19 16:43:29', '2009-11-26 16:43:29', 1, 0, 0, '', 3, '2009-11-20 04:13:29', 0, '0.00', ''),
